  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>(Requires attunement by a druid, sorcerer, warlock, or wizard)</em></p><p>You have resistance to cold damage while you hold this staff.</p><p>The staff has 10 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC: @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Item.RpKjTlYASrfqUPVA]{Cone of Cold} (5 charges), @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Item.IBJmWjzbQGu7M4UX]{Fog Cloud} (1 charge), @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Item.WN2LWEljYU6QqnRH]{Ice Storm} (4 charges), or @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Item.fzZnVKLmBMo2f5up]{Wall of Ice} (4 charges).</p><p>The staff regains 1d6 + 4 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff turns to water and is destroyed.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
